---
import Base from "../layouts/Base.astro";
import SectionWrapper from "../components/SectionWrapper.astro";
import Button from "../components/Button.astro";
import Card from "../components/Card.astro";
---

<Base title="Home" description="Elevateo Co helps established business owners scale past $1M.">

  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <SectionWrapper class="pt-16 sm:pt-20 pb-12 sm:pb-16">
    <div class="text-center md:text-left">
      <h1 class="text-hero font-bold text-white mb-6">
        Scale Your Business Past $1M
      </h1>
      <p class="text-body-lg text-text-secondary max-w-2xl mb-8">
        Elevateo Co helps established business owners build the systems, teams, and strategies needed to break through revenue plateaus and scale with confidence.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center md:justify-start">
        <Button variant="primary" size="lg" href="#signup">Get Started</Button>
        <Button variant="secondary" size="lg" href="/courses/">Learn More</Button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </SectionWrapper>

  <!-- Problem / Solution Section -->
  <SectionWrapper width="wide">
    <h2 class="text-h2 text-center mb-10">The Scaling Challenge</h2>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
      <Card>
        <h3 class="text-h3 mb-3">Bottlenecked by You</h3>
        <p class="text-text-secondary">
          Every decision, every client, every fire runs through you. Your business can not grow past your personal capacity without the right systems in place.
        </p>
      </Card>
      <Card>
        <h3 class="text-h3 mb-3">Revenue Plateaus</h3>
        <p class="text-text-secondary">
          You have hit a ceiling. The tactics that got you to $500K will not get you to $1M. Scaling requires a fundamentally different playbook.
        </p>
      </Card>
      <Card>
        <h3 class="text-h3 mb-3">No Clear Roadmap</h3>
        <p class="text-text-secondary">
          Most business advice is aimed at startups or Fortune 500s. There is a gap for established owners who need practical, proven frameworks to scale.
        </p>
      </Card>
    </div>
  </SectionWrapper>

  <!-- CTA Section -->
  <SectionWrapper id="signup" width="narrow" class="text-center">
    <h2 class="text-h2 mb-4">Ready to Scale?</h2>
    <p class="text-text-secondary text-body-lg mb-8 max-w-xl mx-auto">
      Join business owners who are learning to build scalable systems, generate consistent leads, and grow past $1M in annual revenue.
    </p>
    <Button variant="primary" size="lg" href="/courses/">Explore Courses</Button>
  </SectionWrapper>

</Base>
